  <h3>What is StackMonthly?</h3>
  <p>Stack Overflow is one of the best programmer sites out there. Although mainly a Q&amp;A site, there is tremendous learning value in questions asked by others.</p>
  <p>Unfortunately finding good questions in the tens of thousands of questions on each subject is not possible on the site itself.</p>
  <h3>Enter StackMonthly</h3>
  <p>In the grand tradition of Hacker News Monthly and Ruby Monthly, I present StackMonthly. These are collections of best questions on the top topics each month on Stack Overflow.</p>
